_json.title: How to Contour Sagging Jowls
_json.description:
✨As we age our skin changes. So should our makeup and the way we apply it.🙌

Think of contour like spanx…but for your face! 😊

You can add dimension and camouflage those sagging jowls! Contour is like a mini facelift!💁‍♀️

👉🏼Start at the base of your ear and apply contour all along the underside of your jawline. 

This creates a dark shadow which helps to camouflage our loose skin! Blend downwards so you don’t have a harsh line. 

Color I used:

Astoria
